                        <interp inst="t18391216-name-203" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN GULLEFORD</persName>
                  </hi>. I was called, I went out, and called "Stop-thief"—the prisoner was running up Noble-street—I followed him—he was stopped, and gave me the handkerchiefs from his outside pocket—he had got a quarter of a mile from the shop.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner</hi>. I hope you will have mercy.</p>
